commit.message: Allow printing command line when only setting up sandbox.
ga: update to latest versions of actions
Fix @SANDBOX@ substitution in file names on Windows.

Use own symbol instead of libc one for preload tests.

Avoids problems on systems where remove() is versioned.

Addresses #7.
Add set-modification-time, fix inline stdin data.
Explicitly specify encoding for stdout of subcommands.

Merge pull request #6 from bkmgit/patch-1

Use version option
